    • Method Detail

      • initProtocol

        public void initProtocol()
        Position the pure rodents Ery and Nat in the cages for the beginning of the protocol.
        The first line: pures crosses nat x nat and ery x ery
        The second line: crosses nat x ery and ery x nat
        A-The third line: Hybrids from the second line are crossed with themselves
        B-The fourth line: Hybrids from the second line are crossed with pure males
        C-the fifth line: Hybrids from the second line are crossed with pure females
        Then, A,B and C are repeated for hybrids from the fourth line.
        Author J.Le Fur, A.Comte 03/2012
        Specified by:
        initProtocol in interface I_Protocol
